ygData.messageBody:
Hi all. I'm a 12th level ranger on Rodcet Nife.
Wondering what spells I should look for(if any) beyond the
ones I bought at my guild. <br>Right now I
have...<br>Skin Like Wood<br>Endure Fire<br>Snare<br>Flame
Lick<br>Miner Healing<br>Glimps<br>and Lull
Animales<br><br>What else is out there to use at my level? Also, what
level should I start looking for new spells.
<br><br>Zensidhe<br>Wood-Elf Ranger<br>Rodcet Nife<br><br>P.S. What the heck
does Lull Animal DO anyway? It never seems to have an
effect on anything when I cast it.
